organization.title: NHS Southern Derbyshire CCG
organization.description:
The Clinical Commissioning Group brings together the combined expertise of 57 local GP practices, acting on behalf of over 500,000 patients covering Southern Derbyshire. 

The CCG will serve a large and complex population with both urban and rural geography/ demographics, containing a wide spectrum of social deprivation and health needs.
